column5: Saw a number of clearance signs on reels when I was there on Thursday night  Pete Mania Muskie reel  $69 BPS Pro Qualifier Spinning half price $49 (I have several of these already and like them) Browning Medallion Spinning (one size only) $39  There were a few others but I can't remember.
thanks for the heads up. sadly, i blew my reel budget earlier this week. out of curiosity, was the pete maina reel the round one or low profile?
